title: Helene Fischer Christmas song collection GER-ENG musicfromrizzo
description:
Includes selection in mainly lovely German plus great English ones too
and even the truly much enjoyable Feliz Navidad from Spanish talent originally

This singing was done around the time Helene also offered her very best DVD
performance of some gloriously supremely done renditions of The Russian Medley,  
The Power of Love (also done by Celine Dion previously) We do have
these two song performances posted here for you in DivX at a nice
enough bitrate for many, however in addition we plan to post an H.264 6000k video bitrate version of these two song performances from that DVD  (Mut Zum Gefühl-Live) (musicfromrizzo) (we also have the full DVD posted here in full DVD or 4000k MP4 video bitrate 448k AC3 audio version)

Thanks for seeding - danke equally!
Michael Rizzo Chessman
(musicfromrizzo)
